text: Eleasalo Va'alele "Salo" Ale is an American Samoan attorney. He was the 10th Lieutenant Governor of American Samoa from 2021 to 2025. He was Attorney General of American Samoa from 2014 to 2020. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Lieutenant Governors of American Samoa Category:Living people Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
